scripts.fsr: start /b sass -w dev_fsr:out_fsr --style expanded & xcopy /E/I/Y lib out_fsr & xcopy /E/I/Y assets out_fsr & babel "dev_fsr" --minified -w --out-dir "out_fsr"
scripts.one: start /b sass -w dev_one:out_one --style expanded & xcopy /E/I/Y lib out_one & babel "dev_one" --minified -w --out-dir "out_one"
scripts.all: start /b sass -w dev_all:out_all --style expanded & xcopy /E/I/Y lib out_all & babel "dev_all" --minified -w --out-dir "out_all"
